Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right, Saul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do it! Do it, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do it, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a ghost town here!\NEveryone's already there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I know our duty is to ensure the\Ntrain leaves safely, but I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we're late for the party\Nheld for the entire town...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't... run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to Paulie-san's\Nparty no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's Paulie-san's?! I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town is still in the\Nprocess of being restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet Straw Hat is holding\Na big party at Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wedding party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I can't\Njust sit around like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're important to them,\Nsince we witnessed that precious moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Am I wrong?\N--You're not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may even end up having to deliver\Na congratulatory speech! Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us go, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Entrant #9985, Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about the pride of\Nthe man hidden behind the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I was born on the island of snipers! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ I never miss my mark! Lulu lala lu! ♪\N--Yow, yow, yow, yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far from over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's all party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shanks Makes a Move!\NThe Linchpin to the Reckless Era"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Elder Stars! Five Elder Stars!\NSomething terrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet we sent out to the New World\Nthe other day has been defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Red-Haired Shanks and Edward Newgate,\Naka Whitebeard, two of the Four Emperors,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are finally about to make direct contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hair wants to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let him come aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat better have brought good booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the fleet has been defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Red Hair and Whitebeard will be in contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! We don't know\Nwhat will happen next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by on maximum alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destination straight ahead! Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Red Hair is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hair is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greenhorns oughta stay back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unless you wanna get knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knocked out?! What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to the back and stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I guess it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, guys! Say something! Hey!\N--Don't make a fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've just been knocked\Nunconscious, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lack the mettle can't even\Nstay conscious in front of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's got an incredibly strong Haki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me... for the bit of intimidation\NI gave off, since I'm on an enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see your face,\Nthe scar that guy gave me throbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alcohol"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some healing spirits with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to fight.\NThere's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the man who shows up\Nthrowing his Haki around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Red Hair! What'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Marco of the first division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join my gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, what should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like there won't\Nbe a battle. Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This booze is from the West Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cheap stuff, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having traveled around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find nothing's better than the booze\Nmade from the water I grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's booze from my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Garp, Sengoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't that many people\Nleft who know about that era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 22 years. That's just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have worked your way up the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just a young apprentice\Non Gol D. Roger's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were fighting Roger's\Ngang all the time back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and I got acquainted in an unusual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've found you!\NYou can't escape anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna dye that beard of yours blood red!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my nose isn't blood red!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has that funny Red-nose who was\Nwith you kicked the bucket yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Buggy? That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We parted in Loguetown
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the day our captain was executed,\Nand I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to be your subordinate, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he's still a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the time seemed to flash by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many pass down stories about the days when\Nyou and Hawk-Eye used to duel like legends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those days seem like yesterday to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone of your caliber lost\None of his arms in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What enemy did you give your left arm to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't gonna take you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a crew\Nevery bit as good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the greatest\Ntreasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be King of\Nthe Pirates! I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it... on a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, as long as you have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've experienced many battles\Nand received many scars,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the scar that throbs right now is this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't a wound from an adventure\Nor one received from Hawk-Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who gave me this scar\Nwas one of your men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get what I want to say, Whitebeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was quietly waiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't become a\Ncommander or make his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept his true self hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stood in the shadow of the\Ngreat pirate Whitebeard all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, he's gained power\Nand started to make his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he'll aim for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his own will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'll eventually come\Nto take even your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?\NThat's what you came to talk about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's young, you made him\Nyour second division commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that fame and trust\Nmake the matter complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too soon to have those two fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from Blackbeard Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd talk to me like that...\NThat snot-nosed brat sure did grow a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His crime was killing one of his crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the worst sin you\Ncan commit on a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke the golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I let them board my ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are all my sons,\Nno matter how foolish they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can my killed son's soul go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my responsibility to show that idiot Teach
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't make your way in the\Nworld if you lack a moral code, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100 years too soon to tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this reckless era!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Red Hair, that bastard!\NWhat's he doing to the old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. He's not the type\Nto pull a stupid stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever discussion they\Nhad seems to have fallen apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds have... No, the sky has been split!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I got today's newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's talking about Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So it's finally in the news?!\NHey, what's it saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an article that'll determine our fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--W-Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...talking about us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! We have no choice\Nbut to leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! It's not talking about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Not at all?! Is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I thought we had to\Nlive life on the run! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, when the Franky\NFamily went on such a rampage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your grandpa spun\Nthe information by saying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they were regular people\Nwho got dragged into the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think he'd even think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he would, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's Aokiji who did it.\NHe's hard to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates, but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had to live life on the run\Nfrom here on out, I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, they wrote terrible things about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to this, we declared\Nwar on the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even burning down the island\Nwas our doing, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our bounties will go up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think I'll get a bounty, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm the one who's gonna be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A superstar appears."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys happy about it?!\NAre you stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, Iceberg is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ribbit!\N--Hm? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so what, you don't want\Nhelp from the likes of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Can you keep up with my ship design?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? Do you still have the\Nskills after doing demolition for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from Tom's Workers is here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't have to build a ship\Nin a place like this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it's a ship for the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something we can do to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good if you rush through it all\Nby yourself and do a sloppy job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You guys don't have\Nto work on the backstreets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others said that since they\Ncouldn't come, at least we should go help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he was working on a\Nreplacement for that pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand in my way, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll show you\Nthe skills of those at Dock #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky's building a ship for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. You were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then, he's a nice guy after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's a nice guy! Yep, he's a nice guy!\N--I'm looking forward to seeing the new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's a nice guy!\N--Well then, why don't I go\Nout shopping while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when will that ship be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he came by yesterday,\Nhe said he needed five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, four more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strange dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you call that a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the 100 million\NBerries we had in here go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I gave it to them to buy meat\Nand booze and stuff for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave it to them? It was our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was our party, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We don't have much left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can imagine! In the end,\Neveryone in town showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a real blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we got a good deal with the ship,\Nso there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get gorgeous furniture for the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go hunt for a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami! I'm gonna go out and have fun,\Nso give me some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,@#$%&!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, why does water-water\Ncandy taste this good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put it on top of cotton candy and eat it,\NI don't know what'll happen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--My... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Girl in Search of Her Yagara!\NGreat Search in the City of Water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
